---

<section class="py-[120px] bg-surface-container">
    <div class="max-w-[1296px] mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 lg:px-16">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-4 md:gap-8 items-center">
            <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-5 order-2 md:order-1">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
                    <div class="w-10 h-0.5 bg-secondary"></div>
                    <span
                        class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-secondary tracking-widest"
                        >ABOUT THE AUTHOR</span
                    >
                </div>

                <h2
                    class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg text-primary font-bold mb-6 tracking-tight"
                >
                    Glenn Dyer
                </h2>

                <p
                    class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant mb-6 leading-relaxed"
                >
                    Glenn Dyer writes the Conor Thorn series—WWII espionage
                    thrillers praised by Steve Berry, Jack Carr, and Chris
                    Wallace. His five novels combine meticulous archival
                    research with pulse-pounding suspense, placing readers
                    inside history's most dangerous secret operations.
                </p>
                <p
                    class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mb-10 leading-relaxed"
                >
                    Each book in the series is grounded in declassified
                    intelligence records and firsthand wartime accounts—"a
                    perfect fit for fans of Alan Furst."
                </p>

                <a
                    href="/about"
                    class="inline-block border border-outline-variant text-on-surface-variant px-10 py-4 font-label-caps text-label-caps uppercase tracking-widest hover:border-primary hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-200"
                >
                    FULL BIOGRAPHY
                </a>
            </div>

            <div
                class="col-span-12 md:col-span-6 md:col-start-7 order-1 md:order-2"
            >
                <div class="hard-shadow-subtle">
                    <img
                        alt="Glenn Dyer, author"
                        class="w-full h-auto grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700"
                        src="./dad_headshot.jpg"
                    />
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
